translation services
Suppliers of New & Reclaimed Natural Stone Products.
Windsor CastleTop Quality Yorkshire Stone…
Whitehall Stone Sales LTD was established in 1989 and specialises in the quarrying and manufacture of natural stone products for all of your building requirements and projects.
We quarry, cut and sell our own stone, as well as many types of reclaimed stone…
Our dedicated team of helpful staff are on hand to help you with any enquiries you may have.

We supply:
All bespoke masonry (chamfered, bullnosed etc)Sawn paving, walling, heads, cills/sills & coping stoneNatural bed walling stone/brick – pitched, tumbled, darkened, splitRandom Farm dry stone walling & copingsRockery, driveway, feature stoneRiven crazy paving/floor stoneNatural hard York Stone Riven pavingFOR A QUOTE – CALL US NOW ON: 01274 684440The Riven Paving Process

Riven Natural Stone paving is achieved by the excavation of stone from the quarry floor which has been formed over millions of years.
View Splitting ProcessWorks Gallerys
 
In this section we have some examples of work undertaken using our stone products. Pictured: Graceland Randers Elvis Tribute Museum. Stone: pitched face walling stone 
View Our GallerysNew Materials
 
We employ experienced masons and quarry workers who have worked in the stone industry for 30+ years, ensuring we can deliver the best quality workmanship.
